                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8039" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1252</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2581 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中设股份“蛇吞象”式并购悉地设计，是福还是祸？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is it a blessing or a curse for Zhongshe to merge with CCDI through &quot;snake swallowing elephant&quot; M&amp;A?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄辉，孙小钰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏中设集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中设股份；悉地设计；“蛇吞象”式并购；财务风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jiangsu Zhongshe Group Co., Ltd; Shanghai CCDI Engineering Design Consulting Co., Ltd; “snake swallowing elephant” M&amp;A; Financial risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着经济和科技的高速发展，各行各业的竞争愈发激烈，企业通过并购联手合作逐渐成为一种趋势。时隔近三年，中设股份再拟“迎娶”悉地设计，与普通的并购不同，本次并购是以小并大、以弱并强的“蛇吞象”式并购，由于“蛇吞象”式并购高风险高收益特点的存在，此次并购的财务风险不容小觑，这桩延期的“婚事”能否完成还存在不确定性。本案例描述了中设股份和悉地设计的基本情况，以及“蛇吞象”式并购的动因和过程，重点探讨了中设股份“蛇吞象”式并购悉地设计的并购风险，其中风险主要涉及定价风险、融资风险、支付风险和整合风险四个方面。案例旨在引导学生理解和掌握“蛇吞象”式并购的含义及特点、价值评估方法选择、融资方式抉择、各支付方式优缺点等知识点，学会从并购前的定价风险、并购中的融资支付风险、并购后的整合风险三个阶段识别“蛇吞象”式并购的风险。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid development of economy and science and technology, the competition in various industries is becoming intense, and it is gradually becoming a trend for enterprises to join hands in cooperation through M&amp;A. Nearly three years later, Zhongshe proposed to “marry” CCDI, and unlike ordinary M&amp;A, this is “snake swallowing elephant” M&amp;A. Duo to the high-risk and high-yield characteristics of “snake swallowing elephant” M&amp;A, the financial risk should not be underestimated, and there was uncertainty whether this postponed “marriage” could be completed. This case describes the basic situation of Zhongshe and CCDI, as well as the process and motivation of this M&amp;A, and focuses on risk of this M&amp;A, of which the financial risk mainly involves four aspects: pricing risk, financial risk, payment risk and integration risk. The case aims to guide students to understand and master the meaning and characteristics of “snake swallowing elephant” M&amp;A, the choice of value assessment method, the choice of financing method, the advantages and disadvantages of each payment method, and to learn to identify the pricing risk before the M&amp;A, the financing and payment risk during the M&amp;A, and the integration risk after the M&amp;A in three stages.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与资产重组》、《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“蛇吞象”式并购；财务风险管理理论；信息不对称理论；协同效应理论；杠杆理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
